It is legendary for the 911 sports car and has successfully expanded into SUVs with the Cayenne."], "scores": [0.8011444912661156, 0.7202663048119293, 0.6927692283179443, 0.6412873500322818, 0.6410901969662662], "model_name": "bge-large", "document_ids": ["Ferrari", "Lamborghini", "Maserati", "Bugatti", "Porsche"]}}